metadata.name: Unban Iranian NFT Artists on Opensea
metadata.description:
Decentralization is the main purpose of blockchain and the Opensea platform is not in the path, Opensea deleted Iranian artists art collections without any notice.  
the Opensea marketplace is punishing Iranian artists for their government's actions. Iranian artists are not Iran's regime.  
This NFT Collection is a Protest to Opensea Banning Artists due to politics in countries such as Iran, Cuba, Syria, and so on.  
This Collectible is here on ERC-1155 Smart-contract to show that Opensea is centralized but the blockchain is not,  
you can't stop the power of decentralization and this collection will be available on every marketplace supporting the ERC-1155 contract!  
All the income from this collection will be used to make a Decentralized NFT Marketplace For everyone including Iranian Artists so they can continue their NFT Journey in Peace!
